lead_paragraph: A teenage boy named Dodger finds a gang of kids living in a garbage can. Their repulsive "powers," such as continually flowing nasal mucous or a super-human ability to vomit, make them the perfect team to help Dodger fight against his rival for the girl of his dreams.
